Carter, 1871 (dry) BMNH 1895.4.27.1-6 (Fig. 3); dry schizotype ZMB 3046, (including 17 slides); locality Straight Point, 
<normalizedToken id="D30621B17324C87A7678CA18A3DC72A2" originalValue="Budleigh–Salterton">Budleigh-Salterton</normalizedToken>
