0.5
<normalizedToken id="4C84D85589E29734D5F1B0A2B885FDBB" originalValue="–5.2–">-5.2-</normalizedToken>
7 
<normalizedToken id="CA4112DF37A6D8CFB1A1C3151AA2E6D3" originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
(spines included in width).
</paragraph>
